---
title: State Machine — autoMode × ProgramScreen product
description: Combined state machine for the autoMode store and ProgramScreen.
             Shows legal transitions, guards, and side-effects.
created: 2026-06-03
build: auto-mode-wave-dispatch
canon: XLI (diagram_present design input)
---

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> AutoModeOff : initial (localStorage=false or absent)

  state "autoMode=OFF" as AutoModeOff
  state "autoMode=ON" as AutoModeOn

  AutoModeOff --> AutoModeOn : Alt-A / chip click\n[guard: none]\neffect: localStorage.setItem('la_auto_mode','true')
  AutoModeOn --> AutoModeOff : Alt-A / chip click\neffect: localStorage.setItem('la_auto_mode','false')

  state AutoModeOn {
    [*] --> IdleOn

    state "Idle (autoMode=ON)" as IdleOn
    state "AwaitingConfirm" as Confirming
    state "PlanningInFlight" as Planning
    state "ProgramRunning" as Running
    state "ConfirmExpired" as Expired

    IdleOn --> Confirming : Start clicked\n[guard: codenames.length > 0]\n[first dispatch OR idle > 1h]
    IdleOn --> Planning : Start clicked\n[guard: session confirmed within 1h]\neffect: POST /api/program/plan

    Confirming --> Planning : APPROVE\neffect: sessionConfirmed=now; POST /api/program/plan
    Confirming --> IdleOn : CANCEL (or ESC)

    Planning --> Running : 200 response {builds}\neffect: POST /api/program/start with waves
    Planning --> IdleOn : 4xx/5xx or all waves=[]\neffect: show warning toast

    Running --> IdleOn : ProgramDone SSE event received
    Running --> Running : TaskStart SSE → programTasks Map updated\nWaveLive chips render

    IdleOn --> Expired : timer fires (sessionConfirmedAt + 1h < now)
    Expired --> Confirming : Start clicked\n[guard: codenames.length > 0]

    note right of Confirming
      AutoModeConfirmModal shows:
      - list of codenames
      - estimated wave count
      APPROVE → sessionConfirmedAt = Date.now()
      ENTER key NOT bound (G6 PBGC HARD)
    end note

    note right of Running
      programScreenActive = true (HitlModal gate)
      terminal_window_open_count === 0 (P1 PBGC G5)
      WaveDraft: pre-dispatch editable
      WaveLive: read-only post-dispatch
    end note
  }

  state "autoMode=OFF" as AutoModeOffProg
  AutoModeOn --> AutoModeOffProg : chip toggled OFF during Running\neffect: does NOT cancel running program\n(program continues; chip is display state only)
  AutoModeOffProg --> [*]
```
